description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Thunderstorm Beneath the Summit
-Under Mannen Bridge at Fukagawa
-Sundai, Edo
-Cushion Pine at Aoyama
-Senju, Musashi But
-Inume Pass, Kōshū
-Fuji View Field in Owari Province
-Tama River in Musashi Province
-Tsukuda Island in Musashi Province
-Shichiri beach in Sagami Province
name: Masterpieces of World  - Ukiyo-e, Hokusai's Thirty-Six Views of Mt.Fuji Vol.1-
